  <name>Harmonicon</name>
  <summary>Blues harmonica rhythm game</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Harmonicon is a rhythm game for the diatonic blues harmonica. Notes scroll
      toward a hit line and you play them on a real harmonica — the game listens
      to your microphone, detects the pitches in real time, and scores your
      timing and technique.
    </p>
    <p>It includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Two render modes: a 2D note highway and a 3D harmonica view.</li>
      <li>A free-play Jam Session over a rolling 12-bar blues.</li>
      <li>Technique scoring for bends, vibrato, and wah-wah, plus sustained notes.</li>
      <li>A live audio spectrogram.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.tcanabrava.harmonicon.desktop</launchable>

